'''巴利米納'''（{{lang-en|Ballymena}}）是位於[[英國|英國]][[北愛爾蘭|北愛爾蘭]][[安特里姆郡|安特里姆郡]]的一個鎮，也是北愛爾蘭第八大鎮<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ninis2.nisra.gov.uk/public/AreaProfileReportViewer.aspx?FromAPAddressMulipleRecords=Ballymena%40Exact%20match%20of%20location%20name%3A%20%40Exact%20Match%20Of%20Location%20Name%3A%20%20Ballymena%4016%3F |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-09-25 |archive-date=2014-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129052709/http://www.ninis2.nisra.gov.uk/public/AreaProfileReportViewer.aspx?FromAPAddressMulipleRecords=Ballymena%40Exact%20match%20of%20location%20name%3A%20%40Exact%20Match%20Of%20Location%20Name%3A%20%20Ballymena%4016%3F |dead-url=no }}</ref>。巴利米納被認為是北愛爾蘭聖經地帶的中心城市，擁有很大的新教人口社群<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/drugs/Story/0,2763,439125,00.html |title=''The Guardian'' website. |access-date=2015-01-15 |archive-date=2008-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080208122337/http://www.guardian.co.uk/drugs/Story/0,2763,439125,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 

